h3. Problem Definition
When _Unable to access your account?_ action is triggered in JIRA, the public IP address is not showing in the log:

{noformat}
<ip_address> - - [31/May/2016:22:12:41 +0800] "POST /crowd/rest/um/1/resetpassword/request?username=nedhassan HTTP/1.1" 204 - 21773 "-" "NING/1.0"
{noformat}

h3. Suggested Solution
Provide the ability to display the public IP addresses in the Audit Log or JIRA log itself when _Unable to access your account?_ is triggered. This is important in order to track any unauthorized access to JIRA.

